* Conditional Logic\nin Task Flows
** If/Else Branching
***_ Choose between processing paths
***_ Evaluates expressions
***_ Uses task values or parameters
***_ True/false route execution
** Run If Conditions
***_ Based on upstream task outcomes
***_ Not data value comparisons
***_ Run notification on failure
***_ Cleanup on any outcome
** Use Cases
***_ Data quality threshold routing
***_ Error handling workflows
***_ Remediation pipelines
***_ Alternative data sources
@endmindmap
